data.description: Adorable ranch style home on a beautiful tree lined street! This 3 bed 1 bath home sits on almost half an acre! The owners have beautifully maintained it throughout the years. Some updates include a brand new bathroom, hard wood floors, the carpets in the bedrooms. The house has also been freshly painted.  The new owners will enjoy sitting in the beautiful sunroom letting the sun shine in and just relaxing. The front and back yard are beautifully landscaped.  More pictures to come!
